And do yourself a favor and DON'T get one of those rectangular, 
Facet-style $25 electric fuel pumps.  Even mounted to the frame rail 
with rubber isolators, the constant hammering noise is annoying.  There 
are rotary pumps available in the $50 range that are much quieter.

-David

